  abstract = {We conduct a computational reproduction and a robustness replication of Car- rera et al. (2022) by using the same dataset and similar procedures as specified in their paper (i.e., method and analysis). Instead of using STATA, we use R and code the results from scratch. We also replicate the MATLAB code used for simulations and test whether it produces reasonable results for different parameter values. We confirm all of the main results and do not find high sensitivity of the model to changes in parameters.},
